import { BrowserRouter,Routes,Route } from 'react-router-dom'

import Header from './Header'


function App(){
    return(
    <BrowserRouter>
        <Header />
        <Routes>
            <Route path='/' element="首頁">首頁</Route>
            <Route path='/signin' element="Signin">註冊登入</Route>
        </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter> 
    )
}

export default App
